vote_average":1.75},{"width":2000,"height":3000,"file_path":"/oyNm7fVVtidR4BXTHuAEkHx7XEc.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":1.75},{"width":1000,"height":1500,"file_path":"/oe46YN8oh2gu9CItKaxOaSiJupl.jpg","iso_639_1":"de","vote_average":1.75},{"width":1000,"height":1500,"file_path":"/nZ3XTA5ZlGOj92jRBSYglW8r9QY.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":1.75},{"width":1000,"height":1500,"file_path":"/eRoPafedSvdo17pSmRZULIyGmZB.jpg","iso_639_1":"de","vote_average":1.75},{"width":1200,"height":1800,"file_path":"/iGiO4oFADDLoZINn84EY6ID8FRH.jpg","iso_639_1":"fr","vote_average":1.75},{"width":950,"height":1426,"file_path":"/k7jIYt37BnON8NmncfpN2uRTXSX.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":1.434}],"backdrops":[{"width":1417,"height":797,"file_path":"/rzGHVq2BCMwjp93QaKYoLPSaSrp.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/az0vED4EHaBAEKD6dYNI4UgNgib.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/hRO5xVabFPg5cAgYd60IQUdM0AJ.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/k48RHv98gIMoAnlYGIGz8ogOSEY.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/6yHC73p2i7V1RaaJR2cKKmfJZ9H.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/2LF9eBYwsrgUEYvt3wiMmRBqaSr.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1440,"height":810,"file_path":"/q6JZTL2wQoO3mtCKjsK5ojeozT6.jpg","iso_639_1":"it","vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/chktcP9H2bkHcThy7ZtAQdtmEXH.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/6RC9HlsfvqxfCgN3yD6aPOwBiUq.jpg","iso_639_1":"ru","vote_average":0},{"width":2064,"height":1161,"file_path":"/ed5ovD6veXf1z4qHsmRLdoGJNnf.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":0},{"width":2048,"height":1152,"file_path":"/a1ySuP5BNIitrGDWX7RYTszFhf8.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":0},{"width":2048,"height":1152,"file_path":"/rlUcmFRR5WrwlTNhUHHK3gqz3vE.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T05:16:25.959+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Detective Dee: The Four Heavenly Kings","runtime":132,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dee, the detective serving Chinese empress Wu Zetian, is called upon to investigate a series of strange events in Loyang, including the appearance of mysterious warriors wearing Chiyou ghost masks, foxes that speak human language and the pillar sculptures in the palace coming alive."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Détective Dee : La Légende des rois célestes","runtime":135,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Une vague de crime perpétrée par de mystérieux guerriers masqués terrifie l’Empire de la dynastie des Tang. Alors que le Detective Dee se retrouve en charge de l’enquête, ses découvertes prennent vite une tournure surnaturelle. Les sculptures du palais impérial prennent vie et les quatre rois célestes sont plus menaçant que jamais… Il se pourrait bien que le Detective Dee soit confronté à son plus grand défi, alors même qu’il doit faire face aux accusations de sa pire ennemie, l’impératrice Wu."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"狄仁傑之四大天王","runtime":132,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"大破龍王案後，狄仁傑獲高宗賜「亢龍鐧」，使狄仁傑成為武則天的眼中釘，她命尉遲真金集結「異人組」奪鐧。於此同時，洛陽突現頭戴蚩尤鬼面的神祕組織四處行兇……大唐陷入更深的危機，一場屠魔大戰即將爆發……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Detective Dee e i quattro Re celesti","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Il detective Dee è chiamato a indagare su una serie di strani eventi durante la dinastia Tang in Cina. Mentre si difende dalle accuse di comportamento illecito mosse dall'Imperatrice Wu, la sua più formidabile nemica, un'onda di crimini sconvolge la città, segnata da eventi alquanto misteriosi che vedono i guerrieri indossare maschere, le volpi parlare con linguaggio umano, le sculture del dragone del palazzo imperiale prendere vita e i Re Celesti del tempio mostrare volti arrabbiati. Sembra infatti che tutti siano coinvolti in una cospirazione atta a rendere il caso più difficile che mai per Dee."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"狄仁杰之四大天王","runtime":132,"tagline":"如果我对国产奇幻片还有期待，那一定是因为徐克","homepage":"","overview":"狄仁杰大破神都龙王案后，高宗御赐神器亢龙锏，遭天后武则天嫉妒，天后为盗取亢龙锏陷害狄仁杰，召集了一帮会方术的“异人组”图谋不轨，并命令尉迟真金带队。狄仁杰在医官沙陀忠的帮助下成功摆脱“异人组”迫害，并和尉迟真金商议和解，与此同时“异人组”刺客水月却发现都城出现不明势力，在狄仁杰周旋于武则天的埋伏时，大唐陷入更深的危机，“封魔族”携异术登场，一场“屠魔”大战即将爆发。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Detective Dee und die Legende der vier himmlischen Könige","runtime":132,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Eine Serie höchst ungewöhnlicher Ereignisse ruft erneut Detective Dee auf den Plan. Denn als in den Palästen der Tang Dynastie plötzlich Drachenstatuen zum Leben erwachen, Füchse die Sprache der Menschen beherrschen und mystische Krieger in Masken auftauchen, droht das blanke Chaos auszubrechen. Doch zu allem Überfluss muss sich Dee während seiner Ermittlungen gegen Anschuldigungen seitens der Kaiserin zur Wehr setzen, die ihn ebenfalls in Bedrängnis bringt."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Địch Nhân Kiệt: Tứ Đại Thiên Vương","runtime":0,"tagline":"Detective Dee: The Four Heavenly Kings (2018)","homepage":"","overview":"Địch Nhân Kiệt: Tứ Đại Thiên Vương, kể về những sự việc kỳ lạ liên tiếp xảy ra tại thành Lạc Dương: Một nhóm võ sĩ đeo mặt nạ quỷ Xi Vưu gây án khắp nơi, hồ ly bên ngoài quán rượu hiểu tiếng người, con rồng được khắc trên những cây cột trong hoàng cung sống lại…Địch Nhân Kiệt vừa phải phá giải chân tướng và động cơ của những vụ án thần bí vừa phải nghĩ cách đối phó với sức ép của Võ Hậu khi thời hạn phá án ngày càng gấp…"},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Detective Dee y los cuatro reyes celestiales","runtime":132,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Como recompensa a sus méritos y astucia, el Emperador confía al detective Dee un mazo que da autoridad sobre cualquier persona que amenace la seguridad nacional, incluida la realeza. La Emperatriz sabe que este objeto pone en peligro el equilibrio de poder en la corte, por lo que tratará de hacerse con él, activando una red de conspiraciones que serán solamente la punta del iceberg de la aventura más espectacular del icónico Dee."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"적인걸 3: 사대천왕","runtime":132,"tagline":"역사상 가장 뛰어난 천재 수사관이 돌아온다!","homepage":"","overview":"당나라 최고의 천재 수사관, 적인걸.  신도해왕 사건 이후 황제의 신임을 얻어 항룡간을 하사 받고 대리사의 수장이 된다.  이에 최초의 여황제가 되려는 황후 측천무후는 권력을 차지하기 위해 적인걸을 제거할 계획을 세우고, 근위대장 위지진금에게 항룡간을 빼앗아 올 것을 명령한다.  한편, 적인걸은 수사를 하던 도중 황후의 야심을 이용해 황실에 복수를 꿈꾸는 ‘바람의 전사’의 존재를 알게 되고 피의 복수를 막기 위한 목숨을 건 사투를 시작하는데…"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"狄仁傑之四大天王","runtime":132,"tagline":"地獄不空，誓不成佛","homepage":"","overview":"狄仁傑（趙又廷飾）在大破神都龍王案後，被皇帝（勝鑑飾）御賜神器亢龍鐧，並掌管大理寺，使他成為武則天（劉嘉玲 飾）走向皇權之路最大的威脅，遭到武則天嫉妒，武則天為了盜取亢龍鐧陷害狄仁傑，集結實力強勁的一幫會方術的「異人組」妄圖奪取神器，並命令尉遲真金（馮紹峰飾）協助。狄仁傑在醫官沙陀忠（林更新飾）的幫助下成功擺脫「異人組」迫害，並和尉遲真金商議和解，與此同時「異人組」刺客水月（馬思純飾）卻發現都城出現了不明勢力。狄仁傑既要守護神器，又要破獲神秘奇案，還要面對武則天的步步緊逼，大唐江山陷入了空前的危機之中…"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Детектив Ди: Четыре Небесных царя","runtime":132,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"За заслуги перед отечеством император дарует детективу Ди могущественный артефакт — Жезл Укрощения Драконов. Но императрица недовольна этим жестом, она считает, что таким образом император поставил под угрозу их власть, и Жезл надо немедленно вернуть. Миссия поручается давнему товарищу Ди, а в помощь ему императрица приставляет боевых магов. Но детектив Ди предвидел, что за артефактом начнется охота, и предпринял соответствующие меры."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"ตี๋เหรินเจี๋ย ปริศนาพลิกฟ้า 4 จตุรเทพ","runtime":0,"tagline":"ตี๋เหรินเจี๋ย ปริศนาพลิกฟ้า 4 จตุรเทพ","homepage":"","overview":"หลังจากที่ ตี๋เหรินเจี๋ย  คลี่คลายปริศนาของมังกรทะเล (Sea Dragon) ในตอบจบของภาคก่อน อวี้จื้อเจินจิน (Yuchi Zhenjin) ได้ถูกย้าย และรับการแต่งตั้งเป็นหัวหน้าเดอะโกลเด้นการ์ด ส่วนตี๋เหรินเจี๋ยได้รับความไว้วางใจจากจักรพรรดิเกาจง ให้เป็นหัวหน้าหน่วยสอบสวนและพระราชทานพลองมังกร เพื่อสามารถลงโทษทุกคนที่เป็นอันตรายต่อความมั่นคงของประเทศไม่เว้นแม้แต่ราชวงศ์ ทำให้จักรพรรดินีบูเช็กเทียน (Empress Wu) รู้สึกโดนคุกคาม จึงวางอุบายเพื่อหลอกล่อตี๋เหรินเจี๋ยเพื่อขโมยพลองและโยนความผิดให้เขา งานนี้ ตี๋เหรินเจี๋ยต้องเผชิญกับอุปสรรคมากมายจากจักรพรรดินี บูเช็กเทียน"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Détective Dee : La Légende des Rois célestes","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Une vague de crime perpétrée par de mystérieux guerriers masqués terrifie l’Empire de la dynastie des Tang. Alors que le Detective Dee se retrouve en charge de l’enquête, ses découvertes prennent vite une tournure surnaturelle. Les sculptures du palais impérial prennent vie et les quatre rois célestes sont plus menaçant que jamais… Il se pourrait bien que le Detective Dee soit confronté à son plus grand défi, alors même qu’il doit faire face aux accusations de sa pire ennemie, l’impératrice Wu."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Dedektif Dee 3 : Dört Cennetli Krallık","runtime":132,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Bir çok cinayeti aydınlanmasında büyük rol oynayan Dedektif Dee, işinde son derece profesyonel biridir. Son yaptığı delil araştırmasında istemeden de olsa başı büyük bir belaya girecektir. Çin imparatoriçesi olarak bilinen Wu, dedektifi suçlu görmektedir. Saygın bir kişi olarak bilinen Wu, dedektifin üzerine yıktığı bu suça etrafındaki bir çok kişiyi inandırmıştır. Genç adam ise kendisine atılan bu iftirayı temize çıkarıp kariyerinde tekrar yükselmenin hesabını yaparken nereden nasıl başlayacağı konusunda oldukça zorlanmaktadır. Neticede bu suçlamayı kendisine yönelten bölgenin en önemli isimlerinden biridir."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Detetive Dee: Os Quatro Reis Celestiais","runtime":132,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Sofrendo acusações de uma imperatriz que planeja roubar uma clava domadora de dragões, o magistrado Dee Renjie desvenda uma grande conspiração que ameaça o reino."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Di Renjie Zhi Sidatianwang","runtime":132,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Een golf van misdaden gepleegd door gemaskerde krijgers beangstigt het rijk van de Tang-dynastie. Terwijl Keizerin Wu onder bescherming staat, gaat rechercheur Dee op zoek naar deze mysterieuze misdadigers."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Detective Dee: The Four Heavenly Kings","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":132,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Detektiv Dee blir tvungen att försvara sig när han blir anklagad av kejsarinnan att ligga bakom en kriminell våg som tar sig igen staden..."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Detective Dee: Čtyři nebeští králové","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"V Luo-jangu se dějí záhadné věci: válečníci v maskách rozsévají zločin po celém městě, liška před barem začne mluvit lidskou řečí, draci na sloupech paláce ožívají a nebeští králové ve svatyni se mračí. Dee se musí vypořádat s překážkami, které mu do cesty klade císařovna Wu a rozluštit, co za těmito mysteriózními událostmi stojí."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Detektív Dee: A négy mennyei király","runtime":132,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A Tengeri Sárkány ébredése eseményeit követve, Dee Renjie-t kinevezik a Da Lisi vezetőjének és a császár neki adományozza a Sárkány Szelídítő Jogart. Így, ő lesz a legnagyobb akadálya, hogy Wu Zetian császárné megszerezze a legfőbb hatalmat. A Császárné kijelöli Yuchi Zhenjin-t, hogy a boszorkánymesterek egy csoportját vezetve, vegye el a Jogart Dee nyomozótól. A Wu-Dee konfliktust használva fedezetként, mindenki számára ismeretlenül, egy ősi boszorkány szekta a háttérben azt tervezi, hogy bosszút áll a Tang dinasztián és elpusztítják mindazokat, akik az útjukba kerülnek."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"王朝の陰謀 闇の四天王と黄金のドラゴン","runtime":132,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"前作で国家の危機を救った判事のディーは、その功績により、皇帝から最強の神剣を授けられることに。しかし、それを快く思わない皇后の則天武后は、神剣をわが物にしようと、司法長官のユーチにディーの襲撃を命じ、さまざまな剣術・妖術の使い手である異人組を配下に雇い入れる。そんなある日、宮殿の柱に彫られた巨大な黄金龍に突然生命が宿って大暴れするという奇怪な事件が発生。それは、移魂術を操る封魔族の仕業だった。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Detective Dee: The Four Heavenly Kings","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ဒီဇာတ်ကားမှာတော့ Rise of The Sea Dragon ရုပ်ရှင် အဆုံးကနေပြန်လည်စတင်ထားပြီး ရှင်ဘုရင်က စုံထောက်ဒီးကို နဂါးနိုင်ဓါး (ကျိုင်းတံ) အပ်နှင်းပြီး တစ်တိုင်းပြည်လုံးကို စေခိုင်းနိုင်တဲ့ အခွင့်အာဏာအပ်နှင်းလိုက်တာကနေ စတင်ပါတယ်။ ဒီလို အာဏာ အပ်နှင်းလိုက်တဲ့အတွက် ရှင်ဘုရင်ကို (တရုတ်ပြည်သမိုင်းမှာ တစ်ဦးတည်းသော ဘုရင်မဖြစ်လာမယ့်) မိဖုရားဝူက အမျက်ရှတော်မူပါတယ် စုံထောက်ဒီးလို ဦးနှောက်ပဲရှိပြီး မျိုးရိုးက မင်းမှုထမ်း သာမန်ဖြစ်နေတဲ့ လူမျိုးကို အာဏာအပ်နှင်းရမလား ဆိုပြီးတော့ပေါ့။ ဒါနဲ့ မိဖုရားဝူက ပွဲကြမ်းတော်မူတယ်ပေါ့ ရှင်ဘုရင်ကလဲ သူ့မိဖုရားကို ချစ်ခင်နှစ်သက်တော်မူတာကြောင့် မိဖုရားဝူဟာ ဘုရင်မတစ်ပါးလိုဖြစ်နေတော့ နန်းတွင်းထဲ လုပ်ချင်ရာလုပ်နေသတဲ့။ မိဖုရားဝူအနေနဲ့ကတော့ နဂါးနိုင်ဓါး (ကျိုင်းတံ)ကိုပဲ ပြန်သိမ်းပြီး စုံထောက်ဒီးကို ပညာပေးပါဝါပြချင်ယုံပါ။ ဒါပေမယ့် ရှေ့မင်းဆက်လက်ထက်က ရာဇဝင်ကြွေးမကျေတဲ့ အိန္ဒိယက နတ်ဝိဇ္ဇာ စစ်သည်တော်တွေ မိဖုရားဝူကိုအကြောင်းပြုလို့ ဒီအမှုတွဲထဲကို ပါဝင်လာတဲ့အခါမှာတော့ စုံထောက်ဒီး ဘယ်လိုဖြေရှင်းမလဲဆိုတာ။"},"name":"","iso_639_1":"my","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Burmese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Detetive D e os Quatro Reis Celestiais","runtime":132,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Sofrendo acusações de uma imperatriz que planeia roubar uma clava domadora de dragões, o magistrado Dee Renjie desvenda uma grande conspiração que ameaça o reino."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"დეტექტივი დი: ოთხი ზეციური მეფე","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":97605,"adult":false,"title":"Extracted","video":false,"overview":"Thomas Jacobs invents a way to watch people's memories from the inside. Going against his morals, he accepts an offer to enter a heroin addict's memories to literally see if he committed a crime. However,a malfunction causes his consciousness to become trapped inside the criminal's mind. He remains a prisoner in the addict's memories for more than four years until he discovers the possibility of escape.","genre_ids":[878,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7248,"vote_count":251,"poster_path":"/ciuOIA66tZuCJRfRjfG9coiqjWm.jpg","release_date":"2012-03-10","vote_average":6.215,"backdrop_path":"/WvmaStQ8bInvgFeViOgIBPTDM0.jpg","original_title":"Extracted","original_language":"en"},{"id":48492,"adult":false,"title":"Detective Dee and the Mystery of the Phantom Flame","video":false,"overview":"When the future empress Wu Zetian's two courtiers die in a mysterious fire, she gets Di Renjie, a former detective and rebel, released from prison to solve the mystery of the fire.","genre_ids":[28,12,18,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6924,"vote_count":425,"poster_path":"/qWOBV05kNeLyaiA31DFkZlMpta5.jpg","release_date":"2010-09-18","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/af3gx7Tuu08pf8ioJU0ok6r407J.jpg","original_title":"狄仁傑之通天帝國","original_language":"zh"},{"id":503235,"adult":false,"title":"Hidden Man","video":false,"overview":"A martial arts-infused spy thriller set in 1937 Beijing. A time when China was lurching between revolution, prosperity, and chaos.","genre_ids":[28,80,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7082,"vote_count":81,"poster_path":"/cTq6MDrP4ighdavPDw3xyp8UWw7.jpg","release_date":"2018-07-13","vote_average":6.617,"backdrop_path":"/jNR8Y9e0x8TLHvsBs1RXzVwcnYy.jpg","original_title":"邪不压正","original_language":"zh"},{"id":629210,"adult":false,"title":"Max und die wilde 7","video":false,"overview":"Nine-year-old Max moves to Geroldseck Castle, together with his mother, who takes up a position as a geriatric nurse there. Apparently a shrewd thief is up to mischief here. His mother is suspected, she is threatened with dismissal. Therefore, together with the three residents of the old people's home at table no. 7, Max does everything possible to convict the real perpetrator.","genre_ids":[10751,12,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1287,"vote_count":12,"poster_path":"/sjiiik2oWsc0XW5EXgA2cR3NlDo.jpg","release_date":"2020-08-06","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/mPAJzsGPOgvv4IcqSe0HLPQQ86h.jpg","original_title":"Max und die wilde 7","original_language":"de"},{"id":499152,"adult":false,"title":"The Heiresses","video":false,"overview":"After her girlfriend is imprisoned on fraud charges, Chela is forced to face a new reality. Driving for the first time in years, she begins to provide a local taxi service to a group of elderly wealthy ladies. As Chela settles into her new life, she encounters the much younger Angy, forging a fresh and invigorating new connection.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3042,"vote_count":85,"poster_path":"/tS94bbXmDKIDIoLgBrGJn3Jbwgv.jpg","release_date":"2018-03-15","vote_average":6.459,"backdrop_path":"/6Kvf4BUux2wRuSkUluGmdEWnPXo.jpg","original_title":"Las herederas","original_language":"es"},{"id":157824,"adult":false,"title":"The Smell of Us","video":false,"overview":"Self-destructive teens go skateboarding, use drugs and turn tricks in Paris.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4283,"vote_count":97,"poster_path":"/vKP9PDKRP9x0sDQWHyHdEPJV7YM.jpg","release_date":"2015-01-14","vote_average":4.8,"backdrop_path":"/arUO6RTEyBQFDKPOL3E2e90E9z1.jpg","original_title":"The Smell of Us","original_language":"fr"},{"id":41819,"adult":false,"title":"Deadly Duo","video":false,"overview":"Ah Cheng has decided to get out of this silly kung-fu business and retire with his new girlfriend. Unfortunately, everyone is out to kill him, and one of the killers has been using his trademark knives to frame him! Meanwhile his friends meet up with a mysterious swordsmen who is not what he seems.","genre_ids":[28,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3502,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/mCfXgHBtoNECmOT4lpyxgHaswnB.jpg","release_date":"1978-06-22","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/8ltv1lKZDyeKSygQweHaVovUsq0.jpg","original_title":"雌雄雙煞","original_language":"zh"},{"id":362250,"adult":false,"title":"The Spirit of the Swords","video":false,"overview":"The young swordsman (Nicholas Tse) only for the completion of the master’s last wish before his death – to find ancient Central Plains nine left enduring famous sword, from the north to the Central Plains Penglai. Prior to submission of the court already Martial Shandong, Qingping swordsman and white space Using young swordsman contest Cheat Death, became buried in the court martial of the Black Hand","genre_ids":[18,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3891,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/tWLIxxTMgJ6MILSBYltbH5zaTlx.jpg","release_date":"2015-08-07","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"情剑","original_language":"zh"},{"id":505513,"adult":false,"title":"Detective Chinatown 2","video":false,"overview":"Driven by the desire for the huge reward, Tang Ren tricked Qin Feng to New York, to attend the World Detective Contest. Later on, behind the crazy competition, Qin and Tang discovered the real hidden facts of this contest.","genre_ids":[35,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5023,"vote_count":142,"poster_path":"/p88dG7zfvne14Fn2UHFa2lqijyE.jpg","release_date":"2018-02-16","vote_average":6.261,"backdrop_path":"/2PtF8iqJyac3waFfwNPaCnLrOUn.jpg","original_title":"唐人街探案2","original_language":"zh"},{"id":741674,"adult":false,"title":"The Revenge of the Shiny Shrimps","video":false,"overview":"Two years after the death of Jean, Matthias, the coach, decides to take Selime, a young man from the suburbs he believes is gay, to accompany the Shiny Shrimps to the Gay Games in Tokyo, on a trip to pay tribute to their friend who left too early. But after they miss their connection, they find themselves stranded in Russia, in one of the not the most gay-friendly regions in the world. The start of a crazy adventure as incredible as it is perilous.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.47,"vote_count":94,"poster_path":"/pN7nwsTtpFZKzLizINrQk68QnLx.jpg","release_date":"2022-01-22","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/pAixbe0tvOdAvB8h6AhRTLQQaqv.jpg","original_title":"La Revanche des Crevettes Pailletées","original_language":"fr"},{"id":805627,"adult":false,"title":"Beyond the Infinite Two Minutes","video":false,"overview":"A cafe owner discovers that the TV in his cafe suddenly shows images from the future, but only two minutes into the future.","genre_ids":[35,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9546,"vote_count":281,"poster_path":"/kIKcksbl6dbmxTMS1wq15iFkBnB.jpg","release_date":"2020-06-05","vote_average":7.222,"backdrop_path":"/hiZLoo6joFeqkPZRlvG1zEw5q0.jpg","original_title":"ドロステのはてで僕ら","original_language":"ja"},{"id":420426,"adult":false,"title":"Bleach","video":false,"overview":"High school student Ichigo Kurosaki lives an ordinary life, besides being able to see ghosts and the blurry memories of his mother's death under strange circumstances when he was a kid. His peaceful world suddenly breaks as he meets Rukia Kuchiki, a God of Death.","genre_ids":[28,14,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8377,"vote_count":568,"poster_path":"/hpZVfeJaCilXr9Br7wO9xkfZn7V.jpg","release_date":"2018-07-20","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/oZc9fUwHJ880Q4lFP98s7T5a7Fe.jpg","original_title":"ブリーチ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":9289,"adult":false,"title":"The Longest Day","video":false,"overview":"The retelling of June 6, 1944, from the perspectives of the Germans, US, British, Canadians, and the Free French. Marshall Erwin Rommel, touring the defenses being established as part of the Reich's Atlantic Wall, notes to his officers that when the Allied invasion comes they must be stopped on the beach. \"For the Allies as well as the Germans, it will be the longest day\"","genre_ids":[10752,28,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.8133,"vote_count":998,"poster_path":"/5zmvEofdIlgXrQl9A7e5IOzlnFU.jpg","release_date":"1962-09-25","vote_average":7.6,"backdrop_path":"/yt9FIS2Osm97M7w4dLFkBu7YxW8.jpg","original_title":"The Longest Day","original_language":"en"},{"id":400535,"adult":false,"title":"Sicario: Day of the Soldado","video":false,"overview":"Agent Matt Graver teams up with operative Alejandro Gillick to prevent Mexican drug cartels from smuggling terrorists across the United States border.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.4601,"vote_count":3933,"poster_path":"/qcLYofEhNh51Sk1jUWjmKHLzkqw.jpg","release_date":"2018-06-27","vote_average":6.94,"backdrop_path":"/13VjjUeJ6mcDUB36XRu4YFpYNSm.jpg","original_title":"Sicario: Day of the Soldado","original_language":"en"},{"id":862551,"adult":false,"title":"Me Time","video":false,"overview":"With his family away, a devoted stay-at-home dad enjoys his first me time in years by joining his hard-partying old friend on a wild birthday adventure.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.0394,"vote_count":995,"poster_path":"/bkjPoisqAavXUvtoirxTEcLLQyI.jpg","release_date":"2022-08-26","vote_average":5.854,"backdrop_path":"/5FFpcmPzD5mhLom7bymZq7Py8eT.jpg","original_title":"Me Time","original_language":"en"},{"id":454227,"adult":false,"title":"Outlaw King","video":false,"overview":"Forced into exile by the English after being crowned King of Scotland, legendary warrior Robert the Bruce fights to reclaim the throne.","genre_ids":[28,36,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.0595,"vote_count":1656,"poster_path":"/rT49ousKUWN3dV7UlhaC9onTNdl.jpg","release_date":"2018-09-06","vote_average":6.841,"backdrop_path":"/9uIyOsywwi7bDvHxv3QdiimUtd5.jpg","original_title":"Outlaw King","original_language":"en"},{"id":273895,"adult":false,"title":"Selma","video":false,"overview":"\"Selma,\" as in Alabama, the place where segregation in the South was at its worst, leading to a march that ended in violence, forcing a famous statement by President Lyndon B. Johnson that ultimately led to the signing of the Voting Rights Act.","genre_ids":[36,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.491,"vote_count":2297,"poster_path":"/wq4lhMc4BuOyQqe1ZGzhxLyy3Uk.jpg","release_date":"2014-12-25","vote_average":7.385,"backdrop_path":"/bTnUxw2qH4oBGDMM0w4r6KQ11BD.jpg","original_title":"Selma","original_language":"en"},{"id":823625,"adult":false,"title":"Blacklight","video":false,"overview":"Travis Block is a shadowy Government agent who specializes in removing operatives whose covers have been exposed. He then has to uncover a deadly conspiracy within his own ranks that reaches the highest echelons of power.","genre_ids":[28,53,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.057,"vote_count":1231,"poster_path":"/bv9dy8mnwftdY2j6gG39gCfSFpV.jpg","release_date":"2022-02-10","vote_average":6.155,"backdrop_path":"/tULzz524DuvMxnAuQJpo8dk0EvJ.jpg","original_title":"Blacklight","original_language":"en"},{"id":755898,"adult":false,"title":"War of the Worlds","video":false,"overview":"Will Radford is a top analyst for Homeland Security who tracks potential threats through a mass surveillance program, until one day an attack by an unknown entity leads him to question whether the government is hiding something from him... and from the rest of the world.","genre_ids":[878,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":122.4948,"vote_count":899,"poster_path":"/yvirUYrva23IudARHn3mMGVxWqM.jpg","release_date":"2025-07-29","vote_average":4.199,"backdrop_path":"/iZLqwEwUViJdSkGVjePGhxYzbDb.jpg","original_title":"War of the Worlds","original_language":"en"},{"id":463272,"adult":false,"title":"Johnny English Strikes Again","video":false,"overview":"Disaster strikes when a criminal mastermind reveals the identities of all active undercover agents in Britain. The secret service can now rely on only one man - Johnny English. Currently teaching at a minor prep school, Johnny springs back into action to find the mysterious hacker. For this mission to succeed, he’ll need all of his skills - what few he has - as the man with yesterday’s analogue methods faces off against tomorrow’s digital technology.","genre_ids":[28,12,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.7287,"vote_count":2690,"poster_path":"/tCBxnZwLiY1BOKw3tH6AxHZdqPh.jpg","release_date":"2018-09-13","vote_average":6.271,"backdrop_path":"/qw6nuv56NW1JqzMoONlM84Iciwz.jpg","original_title":"Johnny English Strikes Again","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":5174,"adult":false,"title":"Rush Hour 3","video":false,"overview":"After a botched assassination attempt, the mismatched duo finds themselves in Paris, struggling to retrieve a precious list of names, as the murderous crime syndicate's henchmen try their best to stop them. Once more, Lee and Carter must fight their way through dangerous gangsters; however, this time, the past has come back to haunt Lee. Will the boys get the job done once and for all?","genre_ids":[28,35,80],"popularity":6.5597,"vote_count":3615,"poster_path":"/mp9CzKxLa2i7yblMXUrzVfGqsCo.jpg","release_date":"2007-08-08","vote_average":6.483,"backdrop_path":"/ozsLB1HRCN6ZAmJN89pWtoiAwnb.jpg","original_title":"Rush Hour 3","original_language":"en"},{"id":5175,"adult":false,"title":"Rush Hour 2","video":false,"overview":"It's vacation time for Carter as he finds himself alongside Lee in Hong Kong wishing for more excitement. While Carter wants to party and meet the ladies, Lee is out to track down a Triad gang lord who may be responsible for killing two men at the American Embassy. Things get complicated as the pair stumble onto a counterfeiting plot. The boys are soon up to their necks in fist fights and life-threatening situations. A trip back to the U.S. may provide the answers about the bombing, the counterfeiting, and the true allegiance of sexy customs agent Isabella.","genre_ids":[28,35,80],"popularity":7.7866,"vote_count":4477,"poster_path":"/aBQf2vMiCINeVC9v6BGVYKXurTh.jpg","release_date":"2001-08-03","vote_average":6.754,"backdrop_path":"/vPJwn9pp5f58CqdaXU3eOSLoJkl.jpg","original_title":"Rush Hour 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":276090,"adult":false,"title":"Deadly Snail vs. Kung Fu Killers","video":false,"overview":"The epic magical battle between fairies rages on as young martial artist Cheung risks his life to rescue the Sky Mussel Fairy. No good deed goes unpunished, however, and for his daring but foolish antics, Cheung is cast out of his uncle's safe home. Now, Cheung wanders a perilous world of gods and demons. Only his fighting skills can keep him safe.","genre_ids":[28,18,14],"popularity":0.3098,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/xJTTEY72SJNFVjSaCO3XVmCD6RB.jpg","release_da