"Timecop","original_language":"en"},{"id":8845,"adult":false,"title":"Under Siege","video":false,"overview":"A disgruntled ex-CIA operative, his assistant and their assembled group of terrorists seize a battleship with nuclear blackmail in mind. They've planned for every contingency but ignore the ship's cook, former Navy SEAL Casey Ryback—an error that could be fatal.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":2.8116,"vote_count":1678,"poster_path":"/lQ1SvjOQYLtSeUwcWrzqL0qdRoH.jpg","release_date":"1992-10-08","vote_average":6.295,"backdrop_path":"/ihBDaN7OwT7D9DVri8SmxCnuRLB.jpg","original_title":"Under Siege","original_language":"en"},{"id":9053,"adult":false,"title":"DOA: Dead or Alive","video":false,"overview":"Four beautiful rivals at an invitation-only martial-arts tournament join forces against a sinister threat. Princess Kasumi is an aristocratic warrior trained by martial-arts masters. Tina Armstrong is a wrestling superstar. Helena Douglas is an athlete with a tragic past. Christie Allen earns her keep as a thief and an assassin-for-hire.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":2.3926,"vote_count":895,"poster_path":"/gtlai95IERRDgRhPCK0WEuwCRP0.jpg","release_date":"2006-09-07","vote_average":5.256,"backdrop_path":"/m9mdYhZgowQjuF9LQwkoJLMInGf.jpg","original_title":"DOA: Dead or Alive","original_language":"en"},{"id":9056,"adult":false,"title":"Police Story","video":false,"overview":"Officer Chan Ka Kui manages to put a major Hong Kong drug dealer behind the bars practically alone, after a shooting and an impressive chase inside a slum. Now, he must protect the boss' secretary, Selina, who will testify against the gangster in court.","genre_ids":[28,80,35],"popularity":3.1905,"vote_count":1005,"poster_path":"/1eFB0Iy1TMU4VO5hMcoCE064JAT.jpg","release_date":"1985-12-14","vote_average":7.528,"backdrop_path":"/eYDAnSidN4rIEuneS5gEJkTyk3l.jpg","original_title":"警察故事","original_language":"cn"},{"id":8856,"adult":false,"title":"The Karate Kid Part II","video":false,"overview":"Summoned by his dying father, Miyagi returns to his homeland of Okinawa, with Daniel, after a 40-year exile. There he must confront Yukie, the love of his youth, and Sato, his former best friend turned vengeful rival. Sato is bent on a fight to the death, even if it means the destruction of their village. Daniel finds his own love in Yukia's niece, Kumiko, and his own enemy in Sato's nephew, the vicious Chozen. Now, far away from the tournaments, cheering crowds and safety of home, Daniel will face his greatest challenge ever when the cost of honor is life itself.","genre_ids":[12,18,28,10749,10751],"popularity":3.7673,"vote_count":2415,"poster_path":"/k0OwgRR6PNu7h3SiqpCbRdZWNaG.jpg","release_date":"1986-06-18","vote_average":6.335,"backdrop_path":"/7rfcRXbFD0xr8NteNq1hwXUd4Af.jpg","original_title":"The Karate Kid Part II","original_language":"en"},{"id":278583,"adult":false,"title":"Deadly Target","video":false,"overview":"Two Hong Kong cops on leave to Manila take on a group of arms dealers.","genre_ids":[28],"popularity":0.293,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/gOX6xmFj9izd4hvhePTuEjE7Txd.jpg","release_date":"1994-01-01","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"轟天密令","original_language":"zh"},{"id":9495,"adult":false,"title":"The Crow","video":false,"overview":"Exactly one year after young rock guitarist Eric Draven and his fiancée are brutally killed by a ruthless gang of criminals, Draven, watched over by a hypnotic crow, returns from the grave to exact revenge.","genre_ids":[14,28,53],"popularity":5.6527,"vote_count":4426,"poster_path":"/rMMB3v6jYHjsvXRNJYESacoTD7j.jpg","release_date":"1994-05-11","vote_average":7.518,"backdrop_path":"/cLqvQbP2utIKHRonwXnDjY3l1kk.jpg","original_title":"The Crow","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt6869538","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q55609415","instagram_id":null,"rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/detective_dee_the_four_heavenly_kings"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook"